# Students Directory

Each student gets their own folder following this naming convention:

```
LastName_FirstName/
├── resume.pdf          (or .docx, .md, .txt)
├── cover_letter.pdf    (or .docx, .md, .txt)
├── email.pdf           (or .docx, .md, .txt)
└── GRADE_REPORT.md     (generated by Claude after grading)
```

## Adding Students

You can either:
1. Ask Claude to "Add student [First Last]" and it will create the folder
2. Manually create the folder and add their files

## File Formats

Claude can read: .md, .txt, .pdf, .docx
For best results, use .md or .txt formats.
If using .pdf or .docx, paste the content into a .md file in the student's folder.
